title: Epstein files show Elon Musk apparently discussed plans to visit sex offender's island, host him at SpaceX
summary: Elon Musk corresponded with Jeffrey Epstein in 2012 and 2013, according to newly released files, and sought to visit Epstein's island and host him at SpaceX.

title: Amazon asks FCC for extension for Leo satellite internet service
summary: The company needs to bring more of its satellites online so it can begin offering an internet-from-space service that was recently rebranded as Amazon Leo.
